7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"ISO 17025:2015's Five-Step Laboratory Risk Management"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:54+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"The 2017 version of ISO/IEC 17025 certification, which aims for closer alignment with ISO 9001, has made it necessary for laboratories to adopt risk-based"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 17025:2015's Five-Step Laboratory Risk Management"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The 2017 version of ISO/IEC 17025 certification, which aims for closer alignment with ISO 9001, has made it necessary for laboratories to adopt risk-based thinking in regard to their operations. Preventive action was used to address this in earlier editions of the standards, but the addition of risk-based thinking necessitates that the laboratory take a thorough and strategic look at the unique risks and opportunities it faces."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Many laboratories could be unsure of the procedures to be followed in order to detect, assess, and treat risks and opportunities because it is a new need and the standard does not specify how it should be done. The goal of this article is to help laboratories manage risk in accordance with ISO 17025 certification in Dubai."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Read the article How to Conduct an ISO 17025 Management Reviews"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Laboratory Risk Management Process"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Risk is the inability of the laboratory to achieve its goals, such as client satisfaction. Uncertainty, though, can either be a risk or an opportunity. The five steps of the risk management approach for laboratories are described below."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Determine risks and possibilities:"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Management, quality employees, and technical staff should be viewed as a team in the ISO/IEC 17025 certification risk management process. All the potential issues and possibilities that can result from laboratory activities must be listed in this step. At this point, the following techniques—which can be employed singly or in combination—are helpful:"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Brainstorming: It permits the gathering of viewpoints on all internal and external risk sources. The most thorough and accurate risk assessment is ensured by include employees of all ranks in brainstorming sessions. At this point in the process, all suggestions are welcomed and none are rejected."}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Methodical approach: It takes into account both internal and external factors. The inputs and outputs of the process or activity, including management, methodologies, labor, materials, machines, and the environment, are examined in order to identify the sources."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d"]}],"$L1e"]}]}]
a:null
e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"ISO 17025:2015s Five-Step Laboratory Risk Management | WIZMS"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"The 2017 version of ISO/IEC 17025 certification, which aims for closer alignment with ISO 9001, has made it necessary for laboratories to adopt risk-based"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"ISO 17025:2015 certification consultant in Dubai, ISO 17025:2015 certification in Dubai, ISO 17025:2015 certification in UAE"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"ISO 17025:2015s Five-Step Laboratory Risk Management | WIZMS"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"The 2017 version of ISO/IEC 17025 certification, which aims for closer alignment with ISO 9001, has made it necessary for laboratories to adopt risk-based"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/iso-17025-2015-five-step-laboratory-risk-management"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:31:54+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"ISO 17025:2015s Five-Step Laboratory Risk Management | WIZMS"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"The 2017 version of ISO/IEC 17025 certification, which aims for closer alignment with ISO 9001, has made it necessary for laboratories to adopt risk-based"}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L1f","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Analysis of potential future possibilities: It entails the production of numerous situations, including both positive and negative ones (best and worst case scenarios), which serve as the foundation for the development of an acting style. Data that can be gathered, such as through audit reports or consumer comments and complaints, should be the foundation for predicting. As an illustration, client input demanding more tests may be used to spot a chance to expand testing."}]
11:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Strengths, Weaknesses, Opportunities, and Threats analysis. It examines both internal and external elements, such as the distinctive services provided by the laboratory, together with market pressures and competitive positioning."}]
12:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Read the article ISO 17025 Certification Requirements"}]
13:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 2: Assess the danger"}]
14:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"You could choose to carry either a qualitative or quantitative assessment of your risks and opportunities depending on the complexity of your business. For qualitative evaluations, the team would rate each risk as low, medium, or high. The probability that the event would occur and the seriousness of its ramifications (such as whether the laboratory may suffer financial hardship or irreparable harm to its reputation) would determine the level of risk."}]
15:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"In order to make a quantitative assessment, give each risk and opportunity a value based on their likelihood of happening and their severity. The amount of risk can be calculated and determined using 33 or 55 risk matrices, respectively. The laboratory would use different risk and opportunity matrices. For each element, laboratories may give scores between 1 and 3, which, when multiplied, would give risk numbers between 1 and 9. Each element may be given a score between 1 and 5 for a laboratory with more complicated processes, resulting in risk ratings between 1 and 25. The value of the ensuing risk (or opportunity) is listed as low, medium, or high."}]
16:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 3: Prioritize the possibilities and risks."}]
17:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The optimal risk rating at this point should be agreed upon by all parties in order to decide which hazards need to be addressed first, then second, and so on. Rankings may take into account not just the estimated or assigned risk value but also the cost to address the risk and the resources that are available."}]
18:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 4: Choose the course of action."}]
19:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"To handle the risks and opportunities identified, the team will have to suggest and choose the appropriate course of action. Because the likelihood of the risk occurring is so remote, actions can range from taking steps to mitigate or eliminate the hazards to doing nothing at all. Not every risk analysis must lead to risk-reduction measures."}]
1a:["$","p","20",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The team may decide to address the simpler problems first in order to cross them off the list, but problems that could pose a serious risk to the laboratory should not be put on hold. It is a good idea to designate a person or people to be in charge of the tasks and a deadline for their completion."}]
1b:["$","p","21",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 5: Carry out, keep an eye on, and follow up"}]
1c:["$","p","22",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The chosen activities must next be put into practice in the lab. The administration of the laboratory will be in charge of making sure that resources are available, that the suggested measures are carried out, and that they are having the desired impact."}]
1d:["$","p","23",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Read the article How to get ISO 17025 Certification in Dubai"}]
1e:["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 17025:2015 certification consultant in Dubai"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 17025:2015 certification in Dubai"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 17025:2015 certification in UAE"}]]}]}]
